proven industry experience in object-oriented methodologies, technology and
programming. In particular, we are looking for experience in C ++, Java,
Java classes, CORBA/EJB (both server and client), Internet protocols,
encryption and authentication algorithms, transactional eCommerce systems,
UNIX/LINUX or QNX operating systems, real-time multimedia programming
